{"id":1734993,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-21T12:47:10.170Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1734993,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Siapa Tak Sayang Laki","overview":"# Who Doesn't Love a Husband  The story follows Yunus who works as a company accountant while his wife Liza is a real estate agent and they have two children. Yunus is forced to tighten his belt in order to support all the family expenses while his wife is extravagant and constantly travels abroad alone. Meanwhile, Yunus's coworkers Ghani and Aziz commit a breach of trust by embezzling RM1 million from the company. They attempt to bribe Yunus but fail due to his honest nature. Yunus meets with his friend Osman and shares his problems. Following his friend's advice, Yunus disappears for almost a week and Liza, who becomes panicked, files a police report. She tries hard to search for her husband everywhere. However, her efforts remain unsuccessful. Yunus disappears without a trace and without any message. Meanwhile, the embezzlement scheme is later exposed when Ghani confesses to his guilt. Yunus wants to return to the embrace of his wife and family.","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":"/wIiRB0lL5j8vw8cticjaVvxAbvP.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2017-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Siapa Tak Sayang Laki","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1062448,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Zahiril Adzim","original_name":"Zahiril Adzim","popularity":0.3655,"profile_path":"/dbBIPozCwznZRj9XEzaBAEy0GzQ.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6a5e9c57c713be2a22b80cf6","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":2271063,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Ozlynn Wa